Rudiments of Vim: Editing ruby
^
---------------------------------------------------

Instructions:
1) anything in backticks: `is an expression` ... that can be executed in vim.
2) The arrow keys have been modified for navigation through the tutorial, you will need to use the home row ( hjkl ) to navigate the text.
3) <cr> indicates pressing *carriage return* aka *Enter*,  <esc> indicates pressing Escape, <Space> for space and so on and so forth. and so on and so forth.
